data.name: 39 (feat. Hatsune Miku)
data.loading_phrase: Written for Hatsune Miku's fifth anniversary, "39" is a pun for multiple reasons. By common pronunciations, 3 and 9 are pronounced as "san" and "kyuu", which can be seen as "thank you", and "39" is about Miku thanking her fans. However, 3 and 9 can also be pronounced as "mi" and "ku", which has led to 39 being considered Miku's number by the Vocaloid fandom.
